    ?book a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book> .
    ?book <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/author> ?poet.
    ?poet a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Poet> .
} 
GROUP BY ?poet
ORDER BY DESC(?bookCount)
LIMIT 1

sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?count) WHERE { { ?uri dbo:location dbr:South_Carolina ; rdf:type dbo:Lake } UNION { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Rivers_and_streams_of_South_Carolina } }

QaldSentence: Chi era chiamato Rodzilla?
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/nick> "Rodzilla"@en }

QaldSentence: Dammi le capitali di tutti gli stati dell'Africa.
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?country dct:subject dbc:Countries_in_Africa ; dbo:capital ?uri }

QaldSentence: Quali ponti sono dello stesso tipo del ponte di Manhattan?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?bridge WHERE { dbr:Manhattan_Bridge dbo:type ?type . ?bridge dbo:type ?type ; rdf:type dbo:Bridge }

QaldSentence: Quante società sono state fondate dal fondatore di Facebook?
sparqlQald: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?c) WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Facebook> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundedBy> ?uri . ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundedBy> ?uri }

QaldSentence: Mostrami i percorsi nel Grand Canyon in cui non ci sono pericoli di inondazioni istantanee.
sparqlQald: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/trailheads> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Canyon> FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/hazards> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flash_flood> } }

QaldSentence: Quale libro ha il maggior numero di pagine?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Book ; dbo:numberOfPages ?n } ORDER BY DESC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
sparqlQueGG: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/numberOfPages> ?numberOfPages } ORDER BY DESC(?numberOfPages) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

QaldSentence: Qual è lo stato più esteso degli Stati Uniti?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dct:subject dbc:States_of_the_United_States ; rdf:type dbo:AdministrativeRegion ; dbo:areaTotal ?area } ORDER BY DESC(?area) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
sparqlQueGG: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/AdministrativeRegion> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/areaTotal> ?areaTotal ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States> } ORDER BY DESC(?areaTotal) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

QaldSentence: Dammi tutti i siti internet di aziende con più di 500000 dipendenti.
sparqlQald: PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT distinct ?web WHERE { ?sub dbo:numberOfEmployees ?obj . ?sub foaf:homepage ?web FILTER( xsd:integer(?obj) > 500000 ) . }

QaldSentence: Quali furono i nomi delle tre navi utilizzate da Colombo?
sparqlQald: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Ship ; dct:subject dbc:Christopher_Columbus ; dct:subject dbc:Exploration_ships }
